This paper focuses on modelling and programming self-assembly of molecules, which falls under the category of computational engineering (cs.CE). The use of Kolgomorov complexity-based techniques suggests a focus on machine learning and data analysis, which could also place this paper in the categories of machine learning (cs.MS) or systems and control (cs.SY). The mention of parameter discovery and variability suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
